{"tid":210357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳習棋王下令查心腹王岐山(中紀委書記)","createTime":"2017-04-21T00:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T12:21:29.000Z","uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ff673c991de5abee63f758baeded4c4ba2e859","tid":210357,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T00:45:09.000Z","msg":"針對近來不斷在海外大爆中國高官貪腐猛料的中國富豪郭文貴，中國外交部昨證實國際刑警組織已對他發佈紅色通緝令。郭文貴昨晚接受美國之音專訪，爆料稱中共高層「習王鬥」，稱公安部常務副部長傅政華曾通過電話，指使在海外的他調查中共政治局常委、中紀委書記王岐山與中央政法委書記孟建柱負面醜聞，包括王岐山妻子姚明珊及妻妹姚明端、外姪姚慶持有海南航空股份的內幕，還說中國國家主席習近平下令查王岐山。但在郭文貴想進一步講述王岐山被查一事時，專訪直播突中斷。事後郭文貴稱美國之音受壓，要中斷直播。<br />\n<br />\n中國官方至今尚未對此做出回應。王岐山一直被視為習近平在推動反腐運動上的頭號要角。根據中央社，郭文貴是北京政泉控股公司負責人，長期滯留美國。他因涉及行賄中國前國家安全部副部長馬建，在2013年12月遭到中共中紀委約談，數日後經過香港逃亡海外。他曾對外爆料中共中央辦公廳前主任令計劃兒子令谷在2012年3月車禍身亡時，中共高層內鬥醜聞等。<br />\n<br />\n就在美國之音預告將專訪郭之際，北京透過國際刑警組織對郭發出紅色通緝令。對此，郭否認行賄，稱已28年不曾使用過中國公民身分，顯示北京欲阻他在專訪中爆料。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴表示，傅政華以他家人、員工和資產為要脅，要他調查王岐山外甥姚慶持有的海南航空近年來的貸款、不動產等資金往來情況。郭透露，傅政華說，這是習近平親自下的令，「因為他不相信王跟孟兩人」。美國之音主持人也透露其北京分社社長遭中國公安部門約談，想要了解專訪細節。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道"},{"pid":"24d3a9c6d3505ef21a1945aa2cd7646fa6b8da4e","tid":210357,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"棋王又捉大棋局<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca54f284906c6acf829b19eb927e9c38b8e0c0e","tid":210357,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T00:51:06.000Z","msg":"【十九大權鬥】傳涉王岐山家族 海航狂走資 全球逾三千億收購<br />\n<br />\n昨日被中國外交部證實已發紅色通緝令的中國富豪郭文貴，昨晚接受美國之音時爆料，指習近平擬查中紀委書記王岐山家族在海南航空集團的利益。今次捲入十九大權鬥的海航集團，近年瘋狂向境外轉移資產，除在香港以天價搶地外，在過去兩年，全球收購資產規模交易總額達到400億美元以上（約合3120億港元），並且在中央已全面堵塞資本外流情況下，仍獲得大開綠燈，令市場人士稱奇。<br />\n<br />\n海航集團近年買海外資產瓣瓣都有，涉及酒店、飛機、找還店、物流、銀行、石油、對沖基金，無所不有。在2016年10月，海航集團旗下的Avolon Holdings以100億美元收購CIT Group的飛機租賃業務，同時以約65億美元收購其持有的約25%希爾頓集團股份，成為最大股東。之前在4月，海航集團宣佈收購全球最大的零售貨幣兌換運營商之一的英國nternational Currency Exchange (ICE)。<br />\n<br />\n海航出手在今年更加頻密，在3月，海航集團增持德意志銀行股份至4.76%，成為第三大股東；以4.46億美元收購英國耆衛保險公司（Old Mutual Plc）旗下美國資產管理公司25%的股份。在4月，以7.75億美元的價格，購入嘉能可的石油存儲和物流業務51%的股權，又公告擬以10億美元收購新加坡物流供應商CWT。<br />\n<br />\n而最令全球政經界關注的，是海航在今年1月，以約2億美元買下美國總統特朗普經濟顧問斯卡拉穆奇(Anthony Scaramucci)持有的對沖基金SkyBridge控股權。該交易被視為中國紅色資本介入美國政壇。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經生活資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！"},{"pid":"b4d9e331a22a29dda26685442e0dbe8521c9a635","tid":210357,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T00:51:14.000Z","msg":"俾D時間雜種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd24c2c83f84462a933e05ad8f469681a97ef2e","tid":210357,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾D時間雜種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803cffb2a93d63a3f97cbd0bec2f95e191e3fe81","tid":210357,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:29:41.000Z","msg":"外面比人圍插，自己入面又爭帝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec42074a82c7e922e95c006bb7cc54daccad4266","tid":210357,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:39:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e3c8445eb16411c8832f351dac3b2b1066d43c9","tid":210357,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"幾時將軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7585828478c4296c2ac104cfc7c9841e78e62b88","tid":210357,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"同個二打六講信唔過自己心腹，唔符合官場邏輯。"},{"pid":"dac1a0a171cd59496af7d8c05f217afe2850854a","tid":210357,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"唔好再貼<br />\n搞到d 5毛係咁推d廢post<br />\n<br />\n令到好多post沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988748b7f14daee052a2a789c51dd6f2f22d8249","tid":210357,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同個二打六講信唔過自己心腹，唔符合官場邏輯。</blockquote><br />\n海航邊個話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452c4267c69a31a77c92f0eb6eafa56bf04c99f7","tid":210357,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:49:56.000Z","msg":"海航仲握到香港D地天咁高<br />\n棋王快手收伏佢"},{"pid":"482d52ef4bb4709ebdfb4141c272666a91ae10bf","tid":210357,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33f42e2f7f839795c25caba9e8d7ff844f98583","tid":210357,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好再貼<br />\n搞到d 5毛係咁推d廢post<br />\n<br />\n令到好多post沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b0889a94a6c1fd65507c5330738bad20c180c5","tid":210357,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075c045a350d48d247daf698a2da957394db8489","tid":210357,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"棋王又神之一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761f12ec04f10d7d7a9dc47315913f18b243581d","tid":210357,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:42:05.000Z","msg":"　有一回，一封告密信送到武則天手裡，內容竟是告發周興與人聯絡謀反。武則天大怒，責令來俊臣嚴查此事。來俊臣，心裡直犯嘀咕，他想，周興是個狡猾奸詐之徒，僅憑一封告密信，是無法讓他說實話的；可萬一查不出結果，太后怪罪下來，我來俊臣也擔待不起呀。這可怎麼辦呢？苦苦思索半天，終於想出一條妙計。<br />\n　　他準備了一桌豐盛的酒席，把周興請到自己家裡。兩個人你勸我喝，邊喝邊聊。酒過三巡，來俊臣歎口氣說：「兄弟我平日辦案，常遇到一些犯人死不認罪，不知老兄有何辦法？」周興得意地說：「這還不好辦！」說著端起酒杯抿了一口。來俊臣立刻裝出很懇切的樣子說：「哦，請快快指教。」周興陰笑著說：「你找一個大甕，四周用炭火烤熱，再讓犯人進到甕裡，你找一個大甕，四周用炭火烤熱，再讓犯人進到甕裡，你想想，還有什麼犯人不招供呢？」來俊臣連連點頭稱是，隨即命人抬來一口大甕，按周興說的那樣，在四周點上炭火，然後回頭對周興說：「宮裡有人密告你謀反，上邊命我嚴查。對不起，現在就請老兄自己鑽進甕裡吧。」周興一聽，手裡的酒杯啪噠掉在地上，跟著又撲通一聲跪倒在地，連連磕頭說：「我有罪，我有罪，我招供。」<br />\n　　故事見於《資治通鑒‧唐則天皇后天授二年》。成語「請君入甕」，比喻用某人整治他自己。"},{"pid":"618d362ed3a16e9f90ec1229a8858c0a3ada512f","tid":210357,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:46:13.000Z","msg":"屌，估唔到打貪果班最撚貪，唔怪得689貪5千萬咩事都冇啦，原來係貪污同黨，已經比雜核心貪污團伙立入保護傘名單之內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3add7efe367bf3f2a3204d54ef411c413db3b9bb","tid":210357,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:48:03.000Z","msg":"咁港豬仲有得搭UO就好快手啦"},{"pid":"303591517f48bfb7f469cc619e44609866fe8f9a","tid":210357,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:50:11.000Z","msg":"國際刑警組織已對他發佈紅色通緝令，但係美國又唔使俾人拉即係點？<br />\n<br />\n即係有冇申請政治庇護？<br />\n<br />\n國際刑警去邊個做頭話事？"},{"pid":"ec6017026bcf93e06ff94ad924347fd28cf3f242","tid":210357,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:51:46.000Z","msg":"keep your friends close and your enemies closer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43673a8738f68edb23434ef781785e72ece04cd","tid":210357,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好再貼<br />\n搞到d 5毛係咁推d廢post<br />\n<br />\n令到好多post沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ee6341e3ad0f40b4f493ea0764f7c13cc0d215","tid":210357,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4286bfb62188466d56534b5d81a7132b806b64","tid":210357,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"蒼蠅老虎一起打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" 